process.name: Export Queue Test
process.narrative: Exports the content of a work queue into a csv file.

input.name: Queue Name
input.narrative: The name of the queue to add items to

input.name: Data
input.narrative: A collection containing the data, one row for each item to be added

input.name: Defer Until
input.narrative: Optionally, the date/time the new item(s) should be deferred until

input.name: Priority
input.narrative: Optionally, the priority for the new item(s). Lower numbers represent higher priorities. The default is 0.

input.name: Tags
input.narrative: Optionally, a semi-colon-separated set of tags to apply to the queue item(s)

input.name: Status
input.narrative: Optionally, the initial status required of the work queue item(s)

output.name: Item IDs
output.narrative: The IDs of the items which have been added to the queue, in the order of the collection of data passed that was input

field.name: Item ID
field.description: The Item ID of the work queue item

output.name: User Name
output.narrative: The name of the logged in user in the current system

stage.name: Found Item?
stage.narrative: Searches for the XML file in the target directory and compares the process name with the files found in the directory.

input.name: Folder
input.narrative: The folder in which to look for files

input.name: Patterns CSV
input.narrative: The comma seperated list of wildcard patterns

exception.detail: "Export of Queue '" & [Queue Name] & "' failed. The *.csv file was not found after 1 minute of wait."

stage.name: Global Variables
stage.narrative: Global variables can be accessed from any page within the process.

input.name: Enable Events
input.narrative: Flag to indicate that events should be enabled / disabled on the attached instance - defaulted to True

output.name: handle
output.narrative: An integer which can be used to identify the created instance in subsequent actions

input.name: handle
input.narrative: The integer handle identifying the instance on which the required workbook should be opened. The default of zero indicates the currently active instance.

input.name: File name
input.narrative: The path and name of the file which should be opened.

output.name: Workbook Name
output.narrative: The name used by Excel to identify the workbook - usually this is the file name (without the path).

input.name: handle
input.narrative: The integer handle identifying the instance to be closed. Zero indicates the currently active instance.

input.name: Save Changes
input.narrative: True to save the changes to the open workbooks on the instance, False to discard any changes. Default is False.

exception.detail: "Queue Key '" & [Queue Data.Queue Field] & "' was not found."

stage.name: Delete Item
stage.narrative: Attempts to delete an Item for as long as one minute,

input.name: File Name
input.narrative: The full path to the file to delete

exception.detail: "Failed to delete '" & Replace([Export File Path], """", "") & "'. Recorded Exception: " & [Message]

input.name: ID
input.narrative: The ID of the process to kill

output.name: Success
output.narrative: True if Successful, False by default.

input.name: File Name
input.narrative: The name of the file to check

exception.detail: "Release file containing 'Export Queue Test' workqueue was not found."

input.name: ID
input.narrative: The ID of the process to kill

output.name: Success
output.narrative: True if Successful, False by default.
